## What it is

Bilingual (EN/AR) gold-price intelligence platform: live XAU/USD spot-linked reference pricing, AED and local-currency conversion, karat tables (24K–9K), flagship **Tracker**, calculator, methodology, learn, insights, invest, shops, and country/city/karat pages.

## Stack (summary)

- **Front-end:** Static multi-page site, vanilla ES modules, Vite 8 build → GitHub Pages
- **Optional backend:** Node/Express (`server.js`) — JWT, bcrypt, Helmet, rate limiting
- **Data:** Supabase (Postgres + Auth + RLS); runtime JSON in `data/`
- **Automation:** GitHub Actions (20 workflows) + Python scripts under `scripts/python/`
- **Social:** Hourly production X-post (`@GoldTickerLive`) via `post_gold.yml`
- **PWA:** Service worker (`sw.js`) + `manifest.json`

## Architecture (one line)

Browser → static HTML on GitHub Pages → ES modules fetch spot/FX → optional Express `/api/v1/*` → Supabase; Actions fetch/commit `data/gold_price.json` and run alerts/posting.

